 **Appendix A: Proof of conservation of probability**
 Derivation of the equation of continuity: \
 [
 \partial_t\rho = \frac{2}{\hbar}\text{Im}[\psi^*\Delta V_{\ text{wave}}\psi] = 0 \quad (\Delta V_{\text{wave}} \in \mathbb{R})
 \]

